      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition example that presents well and should be a solid driver for the next owner. The exterior appears well-kept overall with only typical age-related blemishes and light cosmetic wear you\u2019d expect on a used vehicle, and the interior is in nice shape with normal signs of use rather than heavy wear. It looks like a car that has been maintained better than average, without pretending to be perfect or fully restored. Buyers can expect a usable, presentable vehicle that feels cared for and ready to enjoy, with the minor imperfections that come with an older used car.",
