    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Priced at $5,900, this vehicle is in poor overall condition and should be approached as a project, fixer-upper, or basic budget driver rather than a clean turnkey example. It runs and drives, but it shows significant age, wear, and neglect, and buyers should expect noticeable cosmetic flaws, a tired interior, and likely mechanical issues or deferred maintenance. This is not a mint or fully sorted vehicle, and it will need work to bring it up to a higher standard. Best suited for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at and is prepared to put time and money into it.",
