      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with honest character? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a project, or a handy runabout. Priced fairly and represented openly, it\u2019s a great chance to get into a car without breaking the bank. If you appreciate a straightforward sale and a vehicle with potential, this one is well worth a look.",
